Statistical analysis results of post - pre training differences

Source: R/data.R
PRE_POST_STATS.Rd

A data.frame containing statistical analysis results of post - pre training differences: NMR body mass, lean mass, fat mass, mass, 1W and 2W of endurance training; absolute VO\(_2\)max; relative VO\(_2\)max; and maximum run speed.

PRE_POST_STATS

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 90 rows and 20 columns.

See also

PHYSIO
